Changes:
  (new) uim_bool
  (new) UIM_TRUE
  (new) UIM_FALSE
Description:
  A boolean type for uim to explicitly indicate intention about values.  A
  true value is represented as (val != UIM_FALSE). i.e. Don't test a value
  with (val == UIM_TRUE).
